{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2aacac0182","title":"谢富治给北京大专院校红代会电话指示","origin":"1967年5月北京玻璃总厂红卫兵联络站编《中央首长讲话（4）》","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9af881eb58","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":26,"articleId":"2aacac0182"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b6d8a885e","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"93cca4665d","name":"谢富治","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"85b13f5c0b","name":"谢富治"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3a73d861d0","type":"title","text":"谢富治给北京大专院校红代会电话指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aacac0182"},{"id":"99a8f8daee","type":"authors","text":"谢富治","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aacac0182"},{"id":"9f8f77abaf","type":"paragraph","text":"一．北大、师大、清华去中学红代会分成两派，一派支持“四·一三”派，一派支持另一派。全部撤回。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aacac0182"},{"id":"2ece73e8d7","type":"paragraph","text":"二．在外地的同志全部撤回。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aacac0182"},{"id":"6479a9cc91","type":"paragraph","text":"三．红代会要团结。现在矛盾很多（指全国）全国的革命委员会受到很大的冲击。要顾全大局，从大方向考虑。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aacac0182"},{"id":"aaab5c92da","type":"paragraph","text":"四．解决问题要自我批评，地院和北大的问题，有些是原则问题，现在放一放，以后解决。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aacac0182"},{"id":"4f7ac8cf5c","type":"paragraph","text":"五．红代会是中央的拳头，不要自己破坏，主要自我批评，学校内部（清华、北大、师大、矿院）争吵，不要提得那么高。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aacac0182"},{"id":"d08bf7cbcd","type":"paragraph","text":"六．当前的大方向是三个方面：（1）批刘邓就是为了本单位的斗、批、改；（2）批旧市委；（3）整风，主要是整无政府主义，搞思想革命化。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aacac0182"}],"page":{"id":"cb8a79d584","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aacac0182","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}